Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如私吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倆五五分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:01:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我認識一些人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這么做他們肯定有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要花六百萬建個時光機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擔心的那幫人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會先去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看著像個歷史迷  是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會去內戰時期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是古羅馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2001年12月8日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1984年3月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我第一次受賄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我會去未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看五年后或十年后的某些人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確保他們過得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1965年5月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天  沃倫·巴菲特接管了伯克希爾·哈撒韋公司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得  造時光機還剩下了一百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把我的那一半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接投到伯克希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后回到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成了十億富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有萬億富翁的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒什么想改變的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我休息好了
