Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當時在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  當時  在想  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我的律師會干死你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得再打一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再打一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉·奧克利律師事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"相信經驗  相信奧克利"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是比爾·奧克利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"相信經驗  相信奧克利"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡  很上口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  你在...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你這是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知道  你打來的話  我必須報警
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  愣頭青
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察對這通電話再清楚不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很可能在監聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實是  此時此刻我就站在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察局的中央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說他們終于抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好  今天你走運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在跟索爾·古德曼的新咨詢律師通話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上我的思路  比爾  你中大獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咨詢律師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要出名了  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來你這么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上趕飛機到內布拉斯加州的奧馬哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有直飛的航班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得在休斯頓轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這錢誰付
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你付  聽  你聽到了嗎  -聽到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當  當  機會在敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊起來開門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  去機場的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-等等  等一下  -我需要你打幾個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便假設
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意接你的案子...
